{"tid":1403241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英懸紅條橋有得諗喎","createTime":"2019-08-03T18:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T03:24:48.000Z","uid":188522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b06bed7a6f31c2f99d28ab7c534f5a6458493be0","tid":1403241,"uid":188522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:07:55.000Z","msg":"有某智庫既fb 寫到<br />\n<br />\n#諸葛振英 眼見黑警有恃無恐，正義難以伸張。「身在曹營心在漢」的前特首梁振英，繼「恥爾為伍」運動引導反對派「抽廣告」後，又生一計。<br />\n<br />\n今日，他倡懸紅百萬尋辱國旗者。這舉動猶如一巴掌大巴大巴摑醒各方社運巴絲：「又話籌款好快，又話籌款好多，點解唔試下好好運用財力！」。<br />\n<br />\n啊～真不愧是被《紐約時報》稱為「港獨之父」，香港社會運動的第一人。<br />\n----------------------------------------<br />\nCY LEUNG:<br />\n<br />\n倡議成立懸賞基金<br />\n借反對修訂《逃犯條例》為名的狂徒侮辱國家、衝擊警察、破壞秩序，肆虐香港，必須繩之以法。我倡議成立懸賞基金，協助警方緝捕，詳情日後奉上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1382719615336493/posts/2211985389076574?s=1021181400&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1382719615336493%2Fposts%2F2211985389076574%3Fs%3D1021181400%26sfns%3Dmo&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvGhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=707237b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1382719615336493/posts/2211985389076574?s=1021181400&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"5e825388010a02b79235000bed3b4eef56ba3516","tid":1403241,"uid":26813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:08:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">sorry借位宣傳<br />\n幫手推俾前線手足睇！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">！！！實用post！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［前線路障快閃團］簡易快速拆鐵欄攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400592</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2b8dd7d3434d39f7cccb169117f26d02564a9fbd","tid":1403241,"uid":266683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:24:48.000Z","msg":"佢走人數<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sK2aUwe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail